## Research and Governance Notice

This repository provides a governed research-to-decision translation framework for applied AI
research. It is intended to support claim extraction, bounded task design, schema validation,
human-gate review, abstention, rejection, and audit-ready decision reconstruction.

Use of this repository does not establish that a research claim is valid, that a source is
authoritative, that a system is safe for deployment, that a regulatory obligation has been
satisfied, or that an institutional decision has been approved.

The repository separates research interpretation from operational authorization. Any deployment,
procurement, institutional adoption, regulatory filing, or production use requires independent
review by the responsible organization and its qualified legal, security, compliance, governance,
domain, and technical authorities.

