## AI Output and Human Review Notice

The project treats AI-generated outputs as intermediate evidence artifacts. AI-generated outputs
should not be treated as final decisions, institutional approvals, validated research conclusions,
or deployment authorizations without human review and documented authorization.

Human reviewers remain responsible for accept, override, reject, and approval decisions recorded
through the human gate or any derivative review process.

